[301798.27355, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Btolerates it (falls through to recompute), but the clean fix is\u001b[67Gwrite-to-temp\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B+ \u001b[38;5;153mmv\u001b[39m.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B3. \u001b[1mHEAD is a trap.\u001b[22G\u001b[22mpxpipe's\u001b[31Gown\u001b[35Gevent\u001b[41Glog\u001b[45Gshows\u001b[51G\u001b[38;5;153mHEAD / → 404\u001b[64G\u001b[39mwhile\u001b[70G\u001b[38;5;153mGET / → \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B200\u001b[39m. If anyone \"optimizes\" the check to \u001b[38;5;153mcurl -I\u001b[39m, it reports permanently down.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BWorth a\u001b[11Gcomment in the script or a no\u001b[41Ge\u001b[43Gin the baseline: \u001b[61Ghe check must\u001b[75Gstay\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BGET.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B4. \u001b[1m\"Today\" is UTC.\u001b[22G\u001b[22m\u001b[38;5;153mts\u001b[25G\u001b[39mis\u001b[28GUTC\u001b[32Gand\u001b[36GI\u001b[38Gmatch\u001b[44G\u001b[38;5;153mdate -u +%F\u001b[39m,\u001b[57Gso\u001b[60Gon\u001b[63Gthis\u001b[68Gbox\u001b[72G(UTC−4)\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe counter visibly resets at 8pm local.\u001b[44GEither accept it or compute\u001b[72Gthe\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Blocal-day →\u001b[15GUTC range.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B5. \u001b[1mLinear scan of events.jsonl.\u001b[35G\u001b[22m27\u001b[38Glines\u001b[44Gtoday,\u001b[51Gbut\u001b[55Ggrep+jq\u001b[63Gover\u001b[68Gthe\u001b[72Gwhole\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfile is O(file). Months of heavy pip\u001b[41Gg → the <100ms budget\u001b[63Gdi\u001b[66Gs\u001b[68Gquietly.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BCheap bound: \u001b[38;5;153mtail -c 2M\u001b[27G\u001b[39mbefore the grep, or make pxpipe ro\u001b[62Gate the file daily\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(rotati\u001b[11Gn is\u001b[16Gthe right long-t\u001b[33Grm answ\u001b[41Gr anyway).\u001b[52G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B6. \u001b[1mWedged-proxy stall.\u001b[26G\u001b[22mC\u001b[29Gnection-refused is instant,\u001b[57Gbut\u001b[61Ga\u001b[63Ghung\u001b[68Gproxy\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(accepting, not answering) costs th\u001b[39G full\u001b[45G1\u001b[48Gcurl cap\u001b[57Gonce per 5s window\u001b[76G—\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bvisible statusline stutt\u001b[56Gcach\u001b[62Gin a backgr\u001b[74Gunded\u001b[23;1H\u001b[20;38H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[301798.286287, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B+ \u001b[38;5;153mmv\u001b[39m.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B3. \u001b[1mHEAD is a trap.\u001b[22G\u001b[22mpxpipe's\u001b[31Gown\u001b[35Gevent\u001b[41Glog\u001b[45Gshows\u001b[51G\u001b[38;5;153mHEAD / → 404\u001b[64G\u001b[39mwhile\u001b[70G\u001b[38;5;153mGET / → \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B200\u001b[39m. If anyone \"optimizes\" the check to \u001b[38;5;153mcurl -I\u001b[39m, it reports permanently down.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BWorth a\u001b[11Gcomment in the script or a no\u001b[41Ge\u001b[43Gin the baseline: \u001b[61Ghe check must\u001b[75Gstay\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BGET.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B4. \u001b[1m\"Today\" is UTC.\u001b[22G\u001b[22m\u001b[38;5;153mts\u001b[25G\u001b[39mis\u001b[28GUTC\u001b[32Gand\u001b[36GI\u001b[38Gmatch\u001b[44G\u001b[38;5;153mdate -u +%F\u001b[39m,\u001b[57Gso\u001b[60Gon\u001b[63Gthis\u001b[68Gbox\u001b[72G(UTC−4)\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe counter visibly resets at 8pm local.\u001b[44GEither accept it or compute\u001b[72Gthe\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Blocal-day →\u001b[15GUTC range.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B5. \u001b[1mLinear scan of events.jsonl.\u001b[35G\u001b[22m27\u001b[38Glines\u001b[44Gtoday,\u001b[51Gbut\u001b[55Ggrep+jq\u001b[63Gover\u001b[68Gthe\u001b[72Gwhole\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfile is O(file). Months of heavy pip\u001b[41Gg → the <100ms budget\u001b[63Gdi\u001b[66Gs\u001b[68Gquietly.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BCheap bound: \u001b[38;5;153mtail -c 2M\u001b[27G\u001b[39mbefore the grep, or make pxpipe ro\u001b[62Gate the file daily\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(rotati\u001b[11Gn is\u001b[16Gthe right long-t\u001b[33Grm answ\u001b[41Gr anyway).\u001b[52G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B6. \u001b[1mWedged-proxy stall.\u001b[26G\u001b[22mC\u001b[29Gnection-refused is instant,\u001b[57Gbut\u001b[61Ga\u001b[63Ghung\u001b[68Gproxy\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(accepting, not answering) costs th\u001b[39G full\u001b[45G1\u001b[48Gcurl cap\u001b[57Gonce per 5s window\u001b[76G—\r\u0