[301798.302829, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe counter\u001b[15Gvisibly\u001b[23Gresets\u001b[30Gat\u001b[33G8pm\u001b[37Glocal.\u001b[44GEither\u001b[51Gaccept\u001b[58Git\u001b[61Gor\u001b[64Gcompute\u001b[72Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Blocal-day → UTC range.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B5. \u001b[1mLinear scan of events.jsonl.\u001b[22m 27 lines today, bu\u001b[55Ggrep+jq\u001b[63Gover the whole\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfile is\u001b[11GO(file). Months of heavy\u001b[36Gpiping\u001b[43G→ the <100ms budget dies quietly.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BCheap\u001b[9Gbound:\u001b[16G\u001b[38;5;153mtail -c 2M\u001b[27G\u001b[39mbefore\u001b[34Gthe\u001b[38Ggrep,\u001b[44Gor\u001b[47Gmake\u001b[52Gpxpipe\u001b[59Grotate\u001b[66Gthe\u001b[70Gfile\u001b[75Gdaily\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(rotation is the right long-term\u001b[36Ganswer anyway).\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B6. \u001b[1mWedged-proxy stall.\u001b[22m Connection-refused \u001b[46Gs instant, bu\u001b[61Ga hung proxy\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(a\u001b[6Gcepting,\u001b[15Gnot\u001b[19Gansw\u001b[24Gring)\u001b[30Gcosts\u001b[36Gthe\u001b[40Gfull\u001b[45G1s\u001b[48Gcurl\u001b[53Gcap\u001b[57Gonce\u001b[62Gper\u001b[66G5s\u001b[69Gwindow\u001b[76G—\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bvisible statusline stutter. Improveme\u001b[41Gt:\u001b[44Grefresh the cache in a backgrounded\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsubshell and always render\u001b[30Glast-known state.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mImprovements / semantics to capture for the baseline itself\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B7. \u001b[1mThe saved metric is token-count, not cost.\u001b[22m Cache reads counted\u001b[69Gat par\u001b[76G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bunderstate \u001b[15Ghe real saving (~10× cheaper); cache\u001b[52Gcr\u001b[55Gates at par\u001b[67Gunderstate\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Btheir cost (1.25×).\u001b[23GSi\u001b[26Gc\u001b[56G\u001b[38;5;153mable_tokens\u001b[39m,\u001b[69Ga\u001b[23;1H\u00