[301799.807329, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bvisible statusline stutter. Improvement:\u001b[44Grefresh\u001b[52Gthe cache in a backgrounded\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsubshell and\u001b[16Galways render last-known st\u001b[44Gte.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mImprovements / semantics to capture for the baseline itself\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B7. \u001b[1mThe saved metric is token-count, not cost.\u001b[49G\u001b[22mCache\u001b[55Greads\u001b[61Gcounted\u001b[69Gat\u001b[72Gpar\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bunderstate\u001b[14Gthe\u001b[18Greal\u001b[23Gsaving\u001b[30G(~10×\u001b[36Gcheaper);\u001b[46Gcache\u001b[52Gcreates\u001b[60Gat\u001b[63Gpar\u001b[67Gunderstate\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Btheir cost (1.25×). Since events carry \u001b[38;5;153mbaseline_cacheable_tokens\u001b[39m,\u001b[69Ga\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcost-weighted\u001b[17Gvariant\u001b[25Gis\u001b[28Gcomputable\u001b[39Gfrom\u001b[44Gthe\u001b[48Gsame\u001b[53Glines\u001b[59G—\u001b[61Gthat's\u001b[68Gthe\u001b[72Gnumber\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe baseline study probably actually wants.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B8. \u001b[1mClamping the total at 0 hides regressions.\u001b[22m For a s\u001b[57Gudy branch sp\u001b[71Gcifically,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Ba negative\u001b[14Gday (proxy costing more than baseline, e.g. lots of\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153mpassthrough_reasons: not_profitable\u001b[39G\u001b[39mt\u001b[41Gaffic)\u001b[48Gis signal,\u001b[59Gno\u001b[62G noi\u001b[67Ge — consider\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Brendering it\u001b[16Gred instead of\u001b[31Gsuppressing it\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B9\u001b[6G\u001b[1mThe counter is glob\u001b[26Gl, not per-session.\u001b[22m It\u001b[49Gsums every clie\u001b[65Gt through the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bproxy. Fine for a box-wi\u001b[56Git as \"this\u001b[68Gsession\u001b[76Gsaved\u001b[23;1H\u001b[20;38H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
