[302249.307516, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Braw tokens to \u001b[1m~219k cost-weighted\u001b[22m — th\u001b[42G honest number, since most raw\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\"savings\" were cache reads.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mNegatives rendered, not clamped (8)\u001b[41G\u001b[22m—\u001b[43Ga\u001b[45Glosing\u001b[52Gday\u001b[56Gshows\u001b[62Gred\u001b[66G\u001b[38;5;153m· ~-4.0k saved\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m(verified with a synthetic day where the pr\u001b[47Gxy cost more than baseline).\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153mprobe_status != \"ok\"\u001b[39m and out-of-range lines are excluded\u001b[60G(also verifi\u001b[73Gd).\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mProxy-global caveat (9)\u001b[22m — d\u001b[33Gcume\u001b[38Gt\u001b[40Gd \u001b[44G the header block al\u001b[65Gngside the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcost-weighting semantics and the wedged-proxy\u001b[49G1s tradeoff (item 6,\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdeliberately left \u001b[22Gs documented-not-fixed).\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mState after verification:\u001b[29G\u001b[22mup\u001b[32G=\u001b[34Ggreen\u001b[40G+\u001b[42Gdim\u001b[46G\u001b[38;5;153m~219.4k saved\u001b[39m,\u001b[61Gdown\u001b[66G=\u001b[68Gred\u001b[72Gdot\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(saved still shown), empty/missing events = dot only, composed\u001b[66Gwi\u001b[69Ging line\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Brend\u001b[8Grs correctly, 14ms war\u001b[31G / 45ms cold.\u001b[45GTest artifacts (\u001b[38;5;153m/tmp/px_synth.jsonl\u001b[39m,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153m/tmp/px_empty.jsonl\u001b[39m, all test caches) remov\u001b[47Gd.\u001b[50G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BOne\u001b[7Gnote\u001b[12Gfor\u001b[16Gyour\u001b[21Gbaseline\u001b[30Gwrite-up:\u001b[40Gthe\u001b[44G0.1×/1.25×\u001b[55Gweights\u001b[63Gare\u001b[67Ghardcoded\u001b[77Gfrom\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcurren\u001b[10G Anthropic\u001b[21Gc\u001b[23Gche \u001b[56G the constant lives in\u