[302617.642564, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mJudgment calls folded in (3, 4, 7, 8, 9)\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m- \u001b[1mGET-only warning (3)\u001b[22m — comment at the check:\u001b[50GHEAD\u001b[55G\u001b[38;5;153m/\u001b[57G\u001b[39mreturns\u001b[65G404\u001b[69Gon\u001b[72Gpxpipe,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bso it must stay GET.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mLocal day (4)\u001b[19G\u001b[22m— \"today\"\u001b[29Gis\u001b[32Gnow\u001b[36Gthe\u001b[40Glocal\u001b[46Gcalendar\u001b[55Gday\u001b[59Gconverted\u001b[69Gto\u001b[72Ga\u001b[74GUTC\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Brange (\u001b[38;5;153mdate -u -d \"$(date +%F) 00:00\"\u001b[39m → +1\u001b[46Gd\u001b[48Gy), g\u001b[54Gep pre-filters\u001b[69Gon\u001b[72Gboth\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bpossible UTC date prefixes, jq does the\u001b[43Gexact ran\u001b[53Ge compare. No more\u001b[72G8pm-local\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bre\u001b[6Get.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mCost-weighted metric (7)\u001b[30G\u001b[22m—\u001b[32Gactual\u001b[39G=\u001b[41G\u001b[38;5;153minput + 1.25·cache_create + \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B0.1·cache_read\u001b[39m; baseline =\u001b[30Gnon-cacheable at 1.0 plus \u001b[38;5;153mbaseline_cacheable_tokens\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39mweighted by the\u001b[19Gc\u001b[21Gche phase the request ac\u001b[46Gually hit\u001b[56G(0.1 if it was mostly a\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Br\u001b[5Gad, \u001b[10Glse 1.25\u001b[19G— i.\u001b[24G. s\u001b[28Gm\u001b[31Gcache lifecycle \u001b[48Gssumed without pxpipe). Rendered\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bwith a \u001b[38;5;153m~\u001b[39m to flag it's an estimat\u001b[36G. E\u001b[40Gfect on real \u001b[54Gata: today went from 908k\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Braw tokens to \u001b[1m~219k cost-weighted\u001b[22m — th\u001b[42G honest number, since most raw\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\"savings\" were cache reads.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mNegatives rendered, not clamped (8)\u001b[41G\u001b[22m—\u001b[43Ga\u001b[45Glosing\u001b[52Gday\u001