[302618.09826, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bread, else 1.25\u001b[19G— i.e. same cache lifecycle\u001b[47Gassumed without pxpipe). Rendered\u001b[K\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1Bith a \u001b[38;5;153m~\u001b[12G\u001b[39mto\u001b[15Gflag it's\u001b[25Gan estimate. Effect on real data: today went fr\u001b[73Gm 908k\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1Baw tokens\u001b[14Gto \u001b[1m~219k cost-weighted\u001b[37G\u001b[22m— the honest number, since most raw\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\"savings\" were cache reads.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mNegatives rendered, not clamp\u001b[36G (8)\u001b[22m —\u001b[43Ga lo\u001b[48Ging day shows red \u001b[38;5;153m· ~-4.0k saved\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m(ver\u001b[8Gfied\u001b[14Gith\u001b[18Ga synth\u001b[26Gtic day\u001b[34Gwhere\u001b[40Gthe\u001b[44Gproxy\u001b[50Gcost\u001b[55Gmore\u001b[60Gthan\u001b[65Gbaseline).\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153mprobe_status != \"ok\"\u001b[39m and out-of-range\u001b[41Glines are excluded (also\u001b[66Gverified).\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mProxy-global caveat (9)\u001b[22m — docum\u001b[37Gnted in the header block \u001b[63Glong\u001b[68Gide the\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcost-weighting semantics\u001b[28Gand the wedged-proxy 1s tradeoff (item 6,\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdeliberately left as documented-not-fixed).\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mState after verification:\u001b[22m up = green + dim \u001b[38;5;153m~219.4k saved\u001b[39m,\u001b[61Gdown\u001b[66G=\u001b[68Gred\u001b[72Gdot\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(saved\u001b[10Gstill\u001b[16Gshown),\u001b[24Gempty/missing\u001b[38Gevents\u001b[45G=\u001b[47Gdot\u001b[51Gonly,\u001b[57Gcomposed\u001b[66Gwiring\u001b[73Gline\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Brenders correctly, 14ms warm\u001b[32G/\u001b[34G45ms col\u001b[43G. Test artifacts (\u001b[38;5;153m/tmp/px_synth.jsonl\u001b[39m,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153m/tmp/px_empty.jsonl\u001b[24G\u001b[39mall test caches) remove\u001b[48G.\u001b[K\r\u001b